Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.61,0:00:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Licking the penis just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.71,0:00:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.80,0:00:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,To let Mishiro-kun feel good.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.02,0:00:25.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I specially practiced it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.00,0:00:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.66,0:00:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Let it to me, Mishiro-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.05,0:01:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.15,0:01:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I really love you, Mishiro-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.80,0:01:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Mishiro-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.24,0:02:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.38,0:02:39.88,Default,,0,0,0,,She..
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.88,0:02:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That person told me those few words.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.29,0:02:45.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't long.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.36,0:02:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It was the start of the happiest moments of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.41,0:03:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Lying on the rock hard bed, I understood everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.61,0:03:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The moment I reopen my eyes once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.51,0:03:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that I was engulfed really happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.23,0:03:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.59,0:03:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,If only I'd made it earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.53,0:03:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps half of your soul wouldn't have been taken away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.59,0:03:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Who... am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.78,0:03:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Your memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.22,0:03:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe losing your memories is part of your desire.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.21,0:03:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You can call me Kazamidori.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.46,0:03:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Mishiro-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.52,0:03:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Your soul is merely being taken away. It has yet to disappear.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.09,0:03:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Your soul and memories will surely return to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.96,0:04:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That creature will no doubt appear before you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.41,0:04:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,She kept her promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.14,0:04:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,She always stayed by my side from then on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.08,0:04:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Taught me many things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.55,0:04:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,She is my everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.84,0:04:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,She filled the void in my soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.86,0:04:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Those were happy periods where my heart healed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.48,0:04:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But when the Aragami appeared before me once again
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.18,0:04:31.23,Default,,0,0,0,,She died protecting me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.05,0:04:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Tsuina Mishiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.33,0:04:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,A pleasure to meet everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.53,0:04:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Impossible. There's no way it could be her!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.92,0:04:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,She's already dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.75,0:04:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Before my very eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.92,0:05:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet you couldn't understand the lessons having joined midway through.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.90,0:05:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want me to lend you my notes for a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.56,0:05:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be boring being by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.75,0:05:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Should I introduce you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.12,0:05:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We can start with the guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.65,0:05:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show you around the school.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.51,0:05:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.60,0:05:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You've to take into consideration your campus life from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.01,0:05:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you in a daze?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.81,0:05:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you recall some painful memories?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.92,0:05:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,It's normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.55,0:05:41.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.04,0:05:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,He was bullied previously before he moved. Those fellows sure are mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.93,0:05:47.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it true?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.16,0:05:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.24,0:05:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you so uncooperative.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.67,0:05:53.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I was walking on the road before they attacked me suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.37,0:05:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,This city is not as scary as you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.26,0:06:03.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll keep you company when I don't have club activities. Matane~!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.02,0:06:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Now what?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.70,0:06:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.33,0:06:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.76,0:06:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You've yet to even ask me a single question.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.22,0:06:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.58,0:06:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you really so uninterested in me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.60,0:06:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,At least attempt to deny it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.83,0:06:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Yuki, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.50,0:06:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you not?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.22,0:06:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.03,0:06:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuigahama Yuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.24,0:06:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you have anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.68,0:06:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to be frank. Using this kind of attitude won't get you anywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.46,0:06:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't do anything for you,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.70,0:06:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,my heart becomes hazy and won't go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.33,0:06:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't get me wrong! By doing anything, I don't mean kissing or the sort.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.15,0:06:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No lewd intentions.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.04,0:07:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you feel anything?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.89,0:07:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Not even a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.96,0:07:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it, seriously...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.34,0:07:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that? Monsters?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.66,0:07:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see them?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.36,0:07:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.37,0:07:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Look out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.37,0:07:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki is able to see [Kotowari].
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.66,0:08:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.61,0:08:15.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That's!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.91,0:08:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Reishin!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.96,0:08:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,[Kotowari] are fragments of the soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.35,0:08:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Only those whose soul are destroyed can see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.29,0:08:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The only exception are those with deficient soul, that being me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.91,0:08:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What are those?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.46,0:08:37.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know the [Kotowari]?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.19,0:08:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.18,0:08:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Those monsters?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.14,0:08:43.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You see them as monsters?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.11,0:08:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,My family are devout Shintos.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.40,0:08:49.82,Default,,0,0,0,,So I can see ghosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.21,0:08:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,So sorry, Mishiro-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.50,0:08:58.81,Default,,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.81,0:09:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make a move.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.94,0:09:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You blockhead!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.76,0:09:09.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What motives do you harbor coming to see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.79,0:09:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave. Scram at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.59,0:09:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Please listen to what I've to say. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.83,0:09:17.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Granny!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.30,0:09:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That Reishin is a family heirloom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.49,0:09:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,An auntie who looked after her when she was young passed it onto her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.40,0:09:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though she can't remember her very clearly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.02,0:09:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That is Yuki's explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.40,0:09:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Having that sort of reaction after hearing the name Kazamidori.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.46,0:09:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,This place must be connected to Kazamidori-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.72,0:09:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki? No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.12,0:09:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I just said goodbye to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.43,0:09:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Kazamidori-san! Kazamidori-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.26,0:09:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,She can't be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.60,0:10:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Kazamidori-san is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.23,0:10:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I saw it with my own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.28,0:10:21.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop! Please stop! Don't snatch away this power from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.34,0:10:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all that I have. I won't have anything else otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.44,0:10:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I need this power! I've to take it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.68,0:10:34.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't, uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.10,0:10:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't be able to convey your feelings properly to your wife with such a method.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.34,0:10:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Using power of the reishin.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.89,0:10:42.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki is able to touch that fellow's heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.30,0:10:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what she's able to see, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.44,0:10:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Go! Get rid of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.49,0:11:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That was close.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.61,0:11:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.45,0:11:05.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello there.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.76,0:11:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What a beautiful night sky, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.68,0:11:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,The people over there informed me you were harassed by a hoodlum.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.76,0:11:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you all right, Yuki-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.13,0:11:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You're from Granny's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.17,0:11:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave the rest to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.24,0:11:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That person merely wanted to be accepted by others.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.17,0:11:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But no one realizes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.41,0:11:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I know very well, the person who made a mistake is in the wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.69,0:11:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Granny is the person behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.83,0:12:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Mishiro-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.20,0:12:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,She's different.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.82,0:12:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a [Kotowari].
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.25,0:12:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop running!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.38,0:12:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsuina Mishiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.97,0:12:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your fault I'm dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.93,0:12:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Killed by the thing attracted to your abominable left hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.29,0:12:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If only you were dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.51,0:12:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it! Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.20,0:13:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Why would you do something so cruel?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.95,0:13:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Attacking Mishiro-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.13,0:13:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What were you thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.38,0:13:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Answer me, Granny!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.50,0:13:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. I'm so sorry, Mishiro-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.36,0:13:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Kotowari - Fragments of Your Overflowing Heart
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.33,0:13:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I've also become rather nosy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.29,0:13:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,The two of you are always together. How far have you progressed?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.63,0:13:45.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyways, be sure to enjoy what youth is all about. You two.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.72,0:13:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like we've worried Kiyomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.04,0:13:52.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You're pretty close to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.48,0:13:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We talk almost anything, even those which might worry you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.53,0:14:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.69,0:14:08.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I even have dreams, it's pitch black, and the cries of a baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.35,0:14:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough. Don't force yourself to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.36,0:14:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If only Mishiro-kun is always by my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.09,0:14:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.37,0:14:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.99,0:14:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel energize after talking to you, Mishiro-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.32,0:14:36.73,Default,,0,0,0,,So please stay by my side from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.02,0:14:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm even more energetic with that. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.39,0:15:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,How did the cardinal die?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.84,0:15:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,She...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.87,0:15:09.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Granny.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.86,0:15:27.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.35,0:15:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The cardinal protected you, and you met Yuki while at her sanatorium.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.07,0:15:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's considered a miracle for you to be involved in this matter with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.78,0:15:43.56,Default,,0,0,0,,She wasn't able to see [Kotowari] before meeting you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.56,0:15:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're able to see the cardinal now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.81,0:15:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You should somewhat understand the nature of the treatment the cardinal gave you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.98,0:15:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The cardinal filled the void of your soul using her own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.24,0:16:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Kazamidori-san's soul exists within my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.00,0:16:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Because she gave her soul to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.75,0:16:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Kazamidori-san was unable to fight satisfactorily.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.85,0:16:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.17,0:16:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Her soul also exists inside Yuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.11,0:16:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Your heart was transplanted when you were very young.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.41,0:16:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It belongs to the cardinal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.76,0:16:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The day Mishiro-kun transferred to our school.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.38,0:16:26.20,Default,,0,0,0,,My heart skipped a beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.20,0:16:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,If there are remnants of auntie's memories within my heart..
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.79,0:16:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.13,0:16:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You should have realized it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.98,0:16:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You killed the cardinal.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.57,0:16:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Your left arm is able to move
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.88,0:16:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,because your deficient soul still exists somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.13,0:16:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,[Kotowari] are the overflowed fragments of your soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.18,0:16:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.66,0:16:51.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Fragments of Mishiro-kun's soul
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.08,0:16:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,is alive inside the body of the aragami?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.48,0:17:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No! Only those who breed [Kotowari] can see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.96,0:17:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Who do you think the aragami belongs to?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.59,0:17:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's..
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.29,0:17:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,...my [Kotowari].
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.99,0:17:08.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That monster is me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.74,0:17:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you have a fight with Yuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.50,0:17:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,She's really depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.23,0:17:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not a quarrel, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.28,0:17:30.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki is also rather worried now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.79,0:17:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The meeting is at four in the afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.25,0:17:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a shower and get ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.11,0:18:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't forgive myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.08,0:18:09.70,Default,,0,0,0,,For causing Kazamidori-san her death.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.23,0:18:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,We're both dependant on auntie's life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.56,0:18:19.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.20,0:18:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You said you can't forgive yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.68,0:18:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the same for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.83,0:18:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason I'm able to feel so happy now
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.82,0:18:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,is all because of her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.80,0:19:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm only thinking of becoming one with you, Yuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.83,0:20:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.72,0:20:07.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Mishiro-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.98,0:20:35.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Why! Why did it appear again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.45,0:20:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You are me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.37,0:20:38.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you kill her?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.40,0:20:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you kill her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.36,0:20:44.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You are actually me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.89,0:20:47.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it no use even if I beg you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.25,0:20:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I have no use for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.16,0:21:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.13,0:21:16.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.55,0:21:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you prepared to sacrifice your left arm to kill that [Kotowari]?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.92,0:21:24.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm prepared!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.50,0:21:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The cardinal gave me these letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.79,0:21:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Your past is written in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.79,0:21:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I've made contact with the boy burdened with the [Kotowari] we discussed before.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.46,0:21:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The boy is the old lady's grandson.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.58,0:21:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He was taken in by the old lady after his parents died.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.59,0:21:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The old lady used to perform abortions.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.74,0:21:55.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Her hands became unable to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.99,0:21:58.33,Default,,0,0,0,,She thought about it
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.33,0:22:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,but still decided to adopt the boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.43,0:22:04.00,Default,,0,0,0,,She wanted to make use of the boy's slender hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.52,0:22:09.66,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to reverse her own calamity and earn her livelihood.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.29,0:22:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The true nature of the boy's [Kotowari] was revealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.72,0:22:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The [Kotowari] is the boy's consciousness of sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.13,0:22:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,He engulfed countless babies.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.68,0:22:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he killed the souls himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.90,0:22:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The boy came into contact with life.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.89,0:22:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,He felt death within his palms.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.37,0:22:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I persistently urged her to stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.03,0:22:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,The old lady refused to listen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.24,0:22:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,The worst case scenario has to be delivered.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.56,0:22:47.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The boy continue suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.62,0:22:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,He drove out his memories together with his soul
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.29,0:22:53.36,Default,,0,0,0,,in order to protect himself from the terrifying [Kotowari].
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.87,0:22:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That [Kotowari] is still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.15,0:23:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to trace the origins of the aragami, and eliminate his sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.43,0:23:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I resolve myself into doing that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.62,0:23:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do, Kazamidori-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.36,0:23:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Kazamidori-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.20,0:23:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.80,0:23:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.70,0:23:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,You should get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.56,0:23:45.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Kazamidori-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.45,0:23:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry and bring her...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.99,0:23:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Kazamidori-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.84,0:24:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No, don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.52,0:24:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't fight with only vengeance.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.02,0:24:33.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't doubt auntie's words.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.99,0:24:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.75,0:24:38.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That boy is a fragment of your soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.12,0:24:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Only you can accept him.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.30,0:24:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You said to accept him?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.38,0:24:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it shielding?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.05,0:25:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Auntie's [Kotowari] got attacked
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.71,0:25:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,because it's stomach was attacked by her.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.75,0:25:06.08,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to get me back.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.08,0:25:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Weak point...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.59,0:25:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll distract it.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.41,0:25:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Aim for its stomach, Mishiro-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.98,0:25:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't hurt Yuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.99,0:25:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop taking things away from me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.70,0:25:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.53,0:25:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.26,0:25:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Mishiro-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.67,0:25:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.17,0:25:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I've taken many lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.67,0:25:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care what I become.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.28,0:25:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,So I beg of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.80,0:25:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,To send this feeling of life that remains in my hands
Dialogue: 0,0:25:56.64,0:25:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and the pitiful souls
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.10,0:26:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,back to their mothers.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.27,0:26:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,It was always protecting them.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.91,0:26:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Unable to be born.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:13.27,0:26:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The many lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.37,0:26:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,As well as the precious soul of my beloved gentle person.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.87,0:26:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you return them?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.94,0:26:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You've to continue living even with the burden of sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.87,0:26:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I am your sin.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.86,0:26:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.32,0:26:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Take that~
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.42,0:26:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.87,0:27:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Mishiro-kun! Mishiro-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.73,0:27:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.47,0:28:10.84,Default,,0,0,0,,There are still times you're so spoiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.84,0:28:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no helping that, Mishiro-kun.